name: Reduced ferredoxin:dinitrogen oxidoreductase (ATP-hydrolysing)
definition: 16 ATP + 16 H2O + 8 Reduced ferredoxin <=> 8 e- + 16 Orthophosphate + 16 ADP + 8 Oxidized ferredoxin
